==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Specially
<hw>Spe"cial*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>In a special
manner; particularly; especially.</def> <rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>For a particular purpose; <as>as, a meeting of the
legislature is <ex>specially</ex> summoned</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Specialty</ent>⟦br⟧
